com.aevi.magstripe

Interface OnSwipeCallback


  • public interface OnSwipeCallback
    OnSwipeCallback is an interface that is used for creating a callback for use in the MagStripeService.swipe(OnSwipeCallback) method. In the onSuccess the code for handling the results of a mag swipe should be defined. The onFailure should handle to errors that occur when trying to read a swipe. The errorCodes are define in MagStripeError
